Description: The directory under packagePath to serve as source root.

Name: gitUserId
Description: Git user ID, e.g. swagger-api.

Name: gitRepoId
Description: Git repo ID, e.g. swagger-codegen.

Name: artifactVersion
Description: The version to use in the composer package version field. e.g. 1.2.3
